metadata.name: Poor Benedict Brash
metadata.description: First into the breach, MetaExplorers are the vanguard ripping through TPL.  They swarm, battling to be the one to solve the puzzle.  First to defeat any BBEG.  First to reach any destination.  Point them in a direction, then get the hell out of the way.
